        public BuildingEvaluationListener​(Predicate<org.antlr.v4.runtime.ParserRuleContext> predicate)
        Create a building evaluation listener with the given parser rule context predicate.

        The predicate is used to determine which parser rule context(s) should be considered when building the evaluation result tree.

        Parameters:
        predicate - the predicate
